Kirk Byers Templating Links:
https://pynet.twb-tech.com/blog/ansible/ansible-cfg-template.html

Add the .j2 to the end of the file to make that the template file.

/etc/ansible/hosts
[web_servers]
web1 ansible_host=172.20.1.100
web2 ansible_host=172.20.1.101
web3 ansible_host=172.20.1.102

index.html.j2
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

This is a {{inventory_name}} server

</body>
</html>

playbook.yml
---
 hosts: web_servers
 tasks:
   - name: Copy index.html to remote servers
     template:
         src: index.html.j2
         dest: /var/www/nginx-default/index.html
